802 void SP2::Update(double dt)
803 {
804 
805  float LSPEED = 10.f;
806  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('1')) //enable back face culling
807  glEnable(GL_CULL_FACE);
808  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('2')) //disable back face culling
809  glDisable(GL_CULL_FACE);
810  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('3'))
811  glPolygonMode(GL_FRONT_AND_BACK, GL_FILL); //default fill mode
812  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('4'))
813  glPolygonMode(GL_FRONT_AND_BACK, GL_LINE); //wireframe mode
814 
815  //Main menu update or exited main menu
816  if(MenuKey == true)
817  {
818  MenuUpdate(dt);
819  }
820  else
821  LightsReset();
822 
823  if ( Application::IsKeyPressed('E') && police != true && ShopStaff != true)
824  {
825  if ( camera.target.x >= LockerBounds[0]->TTL.x && camera.target.x <= LockerBounds[0]->TTR.x
826  && camera.target.y >= LockerBounds[0]->BTL.y && camera.target.y <= LockerBounds[0]->TTL.y
827  && camera.target.z >= LockerBounds[0]->TTL.z && camera.target.z <= LockerBounds[0]->TBL.z)
828  {
829  ShopStaff = true;
830  ItemMissing();
831  }
832  }
833 
834  //Activate security camera
835  if ( ItemName == "Camera")
836  {
837  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('5'))
838  {
839  camera.setCameraState(1);
840  camera.CameraMode = true;
841  }
842 
843  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('6'))
844  {
845  camera.setCameraState(2);
846  camera.CameraMode = true;
847  }
848  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('7'))
849  {
850  camera.setCameraState(0);
851  camera.CameraMode = false;
852  }
853  }
854 
855  CheckItem();
856  DoorSlide();
857  ShutterOpen();
858  NPCwalk();
859  NPCShop();
860  if (camera.getCameraState() == 0)
861  {
862  CharacterCrouch();
863  UIupdates(dt);
864  BoundsCheck();
865  SetPrevPos();
866  UnpaidItems();
867  camera.Update(dt);
868  Stealing();
869  }
870  else if ( camera.getCameraState() == 1)
871  {
872  Security1.Update(dt);
873  }
874  else if ( camera.getCameraState() == 2)
875  {
876  Security2.Update(dt);
877  }
878 
879  if ( EscapeEnd == true)
880  {
881  ExplosionScale++;
882  }
883 
884  if ( ShopStaff == true)
885  {
886  SInstruct = true;
887  StaffInstructTimer += (1*dt);
888  }
889 
890  //Police spawned alarm rung
891  if ( police == true)
892  {
893  PInstruct = true;
894  PoliceInstructTimer += (1*dt);
895 
896  ROLE = "Thief";
897  ShopStaff = false;
898 
899  /*if ( Application::IsKeyPressed(VK_NUMPAD8))
900  {
901  player.setHealth(1000);
902  }*/
903 
904  if (player.getHealth() <= 0 )
905  {
906  GameEndStealLose = true;
907  }
908 
909  if ( EscapeEnd == true)
910  {
911  EscapeCarMove++;
912  }
913  if ( EscapeCarMove >= 70 )
914  {
915  GameEndSteal = true;
916  keybd_event( VK_NUMPAD9,
917  0X69,
918  KEYEVENTF_EXTENDEDKEY | 0,
919  0 );
920  }
921 
922  if ( GunOffset < 0.06)
923  {
924  GunOffset += 0.01;
925  }
926 
927  if ( GunSwing < 0)
928  {
929  GunSwing +=3;
930  }
931 
932  //Zoom In and out
933  if(Application::IsKeyPressed(VK_RBUTTON))
934  {
935  Mtx44 projection;
936  projection.SetToPerspective(15.f, 4.f / 3.f, 0.1f, 2000.f);
937  projectionStack.LoadMatrix(projection);
938  camera.downSight = true;
939  }
940  else
941  {
942  Mtx44 projection;
943  projection.SetToPerspective(45.f, 4.f / 3.f, 0.1f, 2000.f);
944  projectionStack.LoadMatrix(projection);
945  camera.downSight = false;
946  }
947 
948  //Damage animation reset
949  for ( int i =0; i<PoliceMan.ReadTextFilePoliceSize(); ++i)
950  {
951  if (PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->DamageReset < 0.5 && PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->Damaged == true)
952  {
953  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->DamageReset += (2*dt);
954  }
955  else if (PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->DamageReset >=0.5 )
956  {
957  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->Damaged = false;
958  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->DamageReset = 0;
959  }
960  }
961 
962  //Police respawn
963  for ( int i =0; i<PoliceMan.ReadTextFilePoliceSize(); ++i)
964  {
965  if ( PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->getItemPrice() <= 0 )
966  {
967  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->setItemAvailable(false);
968  }
969  if ( PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->getItemAvailability() == false)
970  {
971  if ( PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->RespawnCD < 20)
972  {
973  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->RespawnCD += (1*dt);
974  }
975  else if ( PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->RespawnCD > 20)
976  {
977  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->resethealth();
978  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->RespawnCD = 0;
979  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->setItemAvailable(true);
980  }
981  }
982  }
983 
984  PoliceShoot(dt);
985 
986  //Police van roll in animation
987  for (int i = 0; i < Police.ReturnListSize(); ++i)
988  {
989  if (Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() == "PoliceVan")
990  {
991  police1.PoliceDrive(Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX(),
992  Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemRotation(),
993  Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ(),
994  80,80,270);
995  }
996  if (Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() == "PoliceVan2")
997  {
998  police2.PoliceDrive(Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX(),
999  Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemRotation(),
1000  Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ(),
1001  -140,80,270);
1002  }
1003  if (Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() == "PoliceVan3")
1004  {
1005  police3.PoliceDriveL(Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX(),
1006  Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemRotation(),
1007  Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ(),
1008  80,-90,90);
1009  }
1010  if (Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() == "PoliceVan4")
1011  {
1012  police4.PoliceDriveL(Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX(),
1013  Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemRotation(),
1014  Police.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ(),
1015  -140,-90,90);
1016  }
1017  }
1018  }
1019 
1020  //Trolley mode activated
1021  if (player.trolley == true)
1022  {
1023  Trolleyz.Position = Vector3(camera.position.x,camera.position.y,camera.position.z);
1024  Trolleyz.Direction = Vector3(camera.target.x-camera.position.x,camera.target.y-camera.position.y,camera.target.z-camera.position.z);
1025  Trolleyz.TrolleyLimiter(camera.position.x,camera.position.y,camera.position.z,dt);
1026  BoundsCheckTrolley(Trolleyz.Position.x,Trolleyz.Position.y,Trolleyz.Position.z);
1027  }
1028 
1029  //Shooting
1030  if (shoot.bullet > 0 && police == true)
1031  {
1032  if(Application::IsKeyPressed(VK_LBUTTON))
1033  {
1034  if (shoot.ShootInterval < 0.3)
1035  {
1036  shoot.ShootInterval += (2*dt);
1037  }
1038 
1039  if (shoot.ShootInterval >= 0.3)
1040  {
1041  CBullet* temp = new CBullet();
1042  temp->Position = Vector3(camera.position.x,camera.position.y,camera.position.z);
1043  temp->Direction = Vector3(camera.target.x-camera.position.x,camera.target.y-camera.position.y,camera.target.z-camera.position.z);
1044  bullet.push_back( temp );
1045  shoot.bullet--;
1046  shoot.ShootInterval = 0;
1047  MusicPlayer.Bullet();
1048  }
1049  }
1050  }
1051  //Bullet check
1052  else if (shoot.bullet <= 0 && police == true)
1053  {
1054  if ( shoot.clip >0)
1055  {
1056  if (shoot.RTime < 2)
1057  shoot.RTime += (1*dt);
1058  if ( shoot.RTime >= 2)
1059  {
1060  //play reloading music
1061  MusicPlayer.Reload();
1062  shoot.clip--;
1063  shoot.bullet=30;
1064  shoot.RTime = 0;
1065  }
1066  }
1067  }
1068  //Reload
1069  else if (shoot.bullet <= 0 && police == true)
1070  {
1071  if ( shoot.clip >0)
1072  shoot.clip--;
1073  shoot.bullet=30;
1074  }
1075 
1076  //Bullet check for delete
1077  for( int i=0; i < bullet.size(); i ++ )
1078  {
1079  BulletCollision(bullet[i]->Position.x,bullet[i]->Position.y,bullet[i]->Position.z,dt);
1080  if ( !bullet[i]->BulletUpdate(dt) || BulletCollision(bullet[i]->Position.x,bullet[i]->Position.y,bullet[i]->Position.z,dt) == true )
1081  {
1082  bullet.erase( bullet.begin() + i );
1083  }
1084  }
1085 
1086  //Enemy bullet check for delete
1087  for( int i=0; i < Policebullet.size(); i ++ )
1088  {
1089  BulletCollisionEnemy(Policebullet[i]->Position.x,Policebullet[i]->Position.y,Policebullet[i]->Position.z);
1090  if ( !Policebullet[i]->BulletUpdatePolice(dt) || BulletCollisionEnemy(Policebullet[i]->Position.x,Policebullet[i]->Position.y,Policebullet[i]->Position.z) == true )
1091  {
1092  Policebullet.erase( Policebullet.begin() + i );
1093  }
1094  }
1095 
1096  //Local calculation for rotation
1097  if ( camera.isCollide == false && player.trolley == true && player.trolleyDrop == false)
1098  {
1099  if(camera.MouseX < 960)
1100  {
1101  DupeRot += (float)(camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1102  }
1103 
1104  if(camera.MouseX < 958 && camera.downSight == false)
1105  {
1106  DupeRot += (float)(18*camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1107  }
1108 
1109  if(camera.MouseX > 960)
1110  {
1111  DupeRot -= (float)(camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1112  }
1113 
1114  if(camera.MouseX > 962 && camera.downSight == false)
1115  {
1116  DupeRot -= (float)(18*camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1117  }
1118  }
1119 
1120  if ( camera.isCollide == false && MenuKey != true )
1121  {
1122  if(camera.MouseX < 960)
1123  {
1124  DupeRotArms += (float)(camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1125  }
1126 
1127  if(camera.MouseX < 958 && camera.downSight == false)
1128  {
1129  DupeRotArms += (float)(18*camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1130  }
1131 
1132  if(camera.MouseX > 960)
1133  {
1134  DupeRotArms -= (float)(camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1135  }
1136 
1137  if(camera.MouseX > 962 && camera.downSight == false)
1138  {
1139  DupeRotArms -= (float)(18*camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1140  }
1141 
1142  if (camera.CameraLock < 40)
1143  {
1144  if (camera.getCameraState() == 0 )
1145  {
1146  if(camera.MouseY < 540 && camera.MouseY >=538)
1147  {
1148  DupeRotArmsY += (float)(camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1149  }
1150  if(camera.MouseY < 538 && camera.downSight == false)
1151  {
1152  DupeRotArmsY += (float)(12*camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1153  }
1154  }
1155  }
1156  if (camera.CameraLock > -40)
1157  {
1158  if (camera.getCameraState() == 0 )
1159  {
1160  if(camera.MouseY > 540 && camera.MouseY <= 542 )
1161  {
1162  DupeRotArmsY -= (float)(camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1163  }
1164  if(camera.MouseY > 542 && camera.downSight == false)
1165  {
1166  DupeRotArmsY -= (float)(12*camera.CAMERA_SPEED * dt);
1167  }
1168  }
1169  }
1170  }
1171  Animate(dt);
1172 }

1201 void SP2::Stealing()
1202 {
1203  if (police == true)
1204  {
1205  Lightswitch = 0;
1206  lights[1].color.Set(1,Lightswitch,Lightswitch);
1207  lights[2].color.Set(1,Lightswitch,Lightswitch);
1208  lights[3].color.Set(1,Lightswitch,Lightswitch);
1209  lights[4].color.Set(1,Lightswitch,Lightswitch);
1210  lights[0].power = 0.1f;
1211  lights[1].power = 1.0f;
1212  lights[2].power = 1.0f;
1213  lights[3].power = 1.0f;
1214  lights[4].power = 1.0f;
1215 
1216 
1217  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT1_COLOR], 1, &lights[1].color.r);
1218  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_LIGHT1_POWER], lights[1].power);
1219  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_LIGHT2_POWER], lights[2].power);
1220  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT2_COLOR], 1, &lights[2].color.r);
1221  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT3_COLOR], 1, &lights[3].color.r);
1222  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_LIGHT3_POWER], lights[3].power);
1223  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT4_COLOR], 1, &lights[4].color.r);
1224  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_LIGHT4_POWER], lights[4].power);
1225  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_LIGHT0_POWER], lights[0].power);
1226  }
1227 }

1236 void SP2::UIupdates(double dt)
1237 {
1238  std::stringstream dd;
1239  dd << camera.position.x;
1240  XPos = dd.str();
1241 
1242  std::stringstream ff;
1243  ff << camera.position.z;
1244  ZPos = ff.str();
1245 
1246  //FPS = 1/dt;
1247  std::stringstream ss;
1248  ss << 1/dt;;
1249  FPS_count = ss.str();
1250 
1251  std::stringstream hh;
1252  hh << camera.target;
1253  Target = hh.str();
1254 
1255  std::stringstream gg;
1256  gg << player.getHealth();
1257  HP = gg.str();
1258 
1259  std::stringstream jj;
1260  jj << player.getStamina();
1261  STAM = jj.str();
1262 
1263  std::stringstream kk;
1264  kk << "$" << player.getMoney();
1265  MONEY = kk.str();
1266 
1267  if ( ShopStaff == true && GameEndStaff != true)
1268  {
1269  DTimer += dt;
1270  std::stringstream DeltaTime;
1271  DeltaTime << setprecision(2) << fixed << DTimer;
1272  DTtime = DeltaTime.str();
1273  }
1274 
1275  if ( GameEndStaff == true)
1276  {
1277  std::stringstream Final;
1278  Final << "Your time :" << setprecision(2) << fixed << DTimer;
1279  EndGame = Final.str();
1280  }
1281 
1282 
1283  std::stringstream Final2;
1284  Final2 << "You stole: $" << player.getMoney() ;
1285  EndGameSteal = Final2.str();
1286 
1287  std::stringstream Final3;
1288  Final3 << "Vehicle Destroyed";
1289  EndGameStealL = Final3.str();
1290 
1291  //Crosshair updates
1292  if ( police == true)
1293  {
1294  std::stringstream ll;
1295  if ( shoot.bullet != 0 )
1296  ll << shoot.bullet;
1297  else if ( shoot.clip > 0 && shoot.RTime == 0)
1298  ll << "Reload";
1299  else if (shoot.RTime > 0)
1300  ll << "Reloading";
1301  else
1302  ll << "Empty";
1303  BulletCount = ll.str();
1304  }
1305 
1306  //Scan for item
1307  for ( int i = 0; i < FNB.ReturnListSize(); ++i)
1308  {
1309  if ( camera.target.x >= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX()-0.2 && camera.target.x <= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX()+0.2
1310  && camera.target.y >= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationY()-1 && camera.target.y <= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationY()+1
1311  && camera.target.z >= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ()-1 && camera.target.z <= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ()+1)
1312  {
1313  ItemName = FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName();
1314  std::stringstream pp;
1315  if ( FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() != "Rifle" && FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() != "Pistol")
1316  {
1317  pp << "$" << FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemPrice();
1318  }
1319  else
1320  {
1321  pp << "Pick Ammo";
1322  }
1323  ItemPrice = pp.str();
1324  break;
1325  }
1326  else
1327  {
1328  ItemName = "";
1329  ItemPrice = "";
1330  }
1331  }
1332 
1333  //scan for cashier
1334  for ( int i = 0; i < 4; ++i)
1335  {
1336  if ( camera.target.x >= cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getTranslationX()-4 && camera.target.x <= cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getTranslationX()+4
1337  && camera.target.y >= cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getTranslationY()-10 && camera.target.y <= cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getTranslationY()+10
1338  && camera.target.z >= cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getTranslationZ()-3 && camera.target.z <= cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getTranslationZ()+3)
1339  {
1340  ItemName = "Checkout";
1341  }
1342  }
1343 
1344  //scan for security camera panel

1383 
1384 void SP2::Animate(double dt)
1385 {
1386  if(walk == false)
1387  {
1388  angle += (float)(WSPEED * dt);
1389  translate += (float)(dt);
1390  if(translate < 0)
1391  {
1392  translateY = translate * -1;
1393  }
1394  else
1395  {
1396  translateY = translate;
1397  }
1398  if(angle >= 30)
1399  {
1400  walk = true;
1401  }
1402  }
1403  else if(walk == true)
1404  {
1405  angle -= (float)(WSPEED * dt);
1406  translate -= (float)(dt);
1407  if(translate < 0)
1408  {
1409  translateY = translate * - 1;
1410  }
1411  else
1412  {
1413  translateY = translate;
1414  }
1415  if(angle <= -30)
1416  {
1417  walk = false;
1418  }
1419  }
1420 }
1421 
1422 void SP2::CharacterCrouch()
1423 {
1424  if(Application::IsKeyPressed(VK_CONTROL) && camera.position.y != 4)
1425  {
1426  camera.position.y -= 0.5;
1427  camera.target.y -= 0.5;
1428  }
1429  else if (Application::IsKeyReleased(VK_CONTROL) && camera.position.y != 6 )
1430  {
1431  camera.position.y = 6;
1432  camera.target.y = 6;
1433  camera.CameraLock = 0;
1434  camera.CamRotationY = 0;
1435  }
1436 }

2243 void SP2::Trolley()
2244 {

2246  {
2247  if ( camera.target.x >= trolley.LastX-5 && camera.target.x <= trolley.LastX+5

2249  && camera.target.z >= trolley.LastZ-5 && camera.target.z <= trolley.LastZ+5)

2259

2261  {
2262  player.setInventoryCap(trolley.ExpansionSize);
2263  modelStack.PushMatrix();
2264  modelStack.Translate(camera.position.x,data.GetRenderPos(21)->getTranslationY(),camera.position.z);
2265  modelStack.Rotate(DupeRot,data.GetRenderPos(21)->getRX(),data.GetRenderPos(21)->getRY(),data.GetRenderPos(21)->getRZ());
2266  modelStack.PushMatrix();

2271  modelStack.PopMatrix();

2273  }
2274 
2275  else if ( player.trolley == false && player.trolleyDrop == false)
2276  {
2277  modelStack.PushMatrix();
2278  modelStack.Translate(data.GetRenderPos(21)->getTranslationX(),data.GetRenderPos(21)->getTranslationY(),data.GetRenderPos(21)->getTranslationZ());
2279  modelStack.Rotate(data.GetRenderPos(21)->getRotation(),data.GetRenderPos(21)->getRX(),data.GetRenderPos(21)->getRY(),data.GetRenderPos(21)->getRZ());

2305 void SP2::TrolleyUpdate()
2306 {
2307  float tempOffsetY = 2;
2308  float offSetZ = 0;
2309  float offSetX = 0;

2314  {

2316  {
2317  if ( i >= 5 )

2612 void SP2::Render()
2613 {
2614  //bool toggleLight = false;
2615 
2616  //clear depth and color buffer
2617  glClear(GL_COLOR_BUFFER_BIT | GL_DEPTH_BUFFER_BIT);
2618 
2619  //Temp variables
2620  Mtx44 MVP;
2621 
2622  viewStack.LoadIdentity();
2623  if ( camera.getCameraState() == 0 )
2624  {
2625  viewStack.LookAt(camera.position.x, camera.position.y, camera.position.z, camera.target.x, camera.target.y, camera.target.z, camera.up.x, camera.up.y, camera.up.z);
2626  }
2627  else if ( camera.getCameraState() == 1 )
2628  {
2629  viewStack.LookAt(Security1.position.x, Security1.position.y, Security1.position.z, Security1.target.x, Security1.target.y, Security1.target.z, Security1.up.x, Security1.up.y, Security1.up.z);
2630  }
2631  else if ( camera.getCameraState() == 2 )
2632  {
2633  viewStack.LookAt(Security2.position.x, Security2.position.y, Security2.position.z, Security2.target.x, Security2.target.y, Security2.target.z, Security2.up.x, Security2.up.y, Security2.up.z);
2634  }
2635  else if ( camera.getCameraState() == 3 )
2636  {
2637  viewStack.LookAt(EndScene.position.x, EndScene.position.y, EndScene.position.z, EndScene.target.x, EndScene.target.y, EndScene.target.z, EndScene.up.x, EndScene.up.y, EndScene.up.z);
2638  }
2639  modelStack.LoadIdentity();
2640 
2641  if(lights[0].type == Light::LIGHT_DIRECTIONAL)
2642  {
2643  Vector3 lightDir(lights[0].position.x, lights[0].position.y, lights[0].position.z);
2644  Vector3 lightDirection_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lightDir;
2645  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT0_POSITION], 1, &lightDirection_cameraspace.x);
2646  }
2647  else if(lights[0].type == Light::LIGHT_SPOT)
2648  {
2649  Position lightPosition_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[0].position;
2650  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT0_POSITION], 1, &lightPosition_cameraspace.x);
2651  Vector3 spotDirection_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[0].spotDirection;
2652  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT0_SPOTDIRECTION], 1, &spotDirection_cameraspace.x);
2653  }
2654  else
2655  {
2656  Position lightPosition_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[0].position;
2657  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT0_POSITION], 1, &lightPosition_cameraspace.x);
2658  }
2659  if(lights[1].type == Light::LIGHT_SPOT)
2660  {
2661  Position lightPosition_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[1].position;
2662  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT1_POSITION], 1, &lightPosition_cameraspace.x);
2663  Vector3 spotDirection_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[1].spotDirection;
2664  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT1_SPOTDIRECTION], 1, &spotDirection_cameraspace.x);
2665  }
2666  if(lights[2].type == Light::LIGHT_SPOT)
2667  {
2668  Position lightPosition_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[2].position;
2669  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT2_POSITION], 1, &lightPosition_cameraspace.x);
2670  Vector3 spotDirection_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[2].spotDirection;
2671  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT2_SPOTDIRECTION], 1, &spotDirection_cameraspace.x);
2672  }
2673  if(lights[3].type == Light::LIGHT_SPOT)
2674  {
2675  Position lightPosition_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[3].position;
2676  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT3_POSITION], 1, &lightPosition_cameraspace.x);
2677  Vector3 spotDirection_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[3].spotDirection;
2678  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT3_SPOTDIRECTION], 1, &spotDirection_cameraspace.x);
2679  }
2680  if(lights[4].type == Light::LIGHT_SPOT)
2681  {
2682  Position lightPosition_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[4].position;
2683  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT4_POSITION], 1, &lightPosition_cameraspace.x);
2684  Vector3 spotDirection_cameraspace = viewStack.Top() * lights[4].spotDirection;
2685  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_LIGHT4_SPOTDIRECTION], 1, &spotDirection_cameraspace.x);
2686  }
2687 
2688  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_AXES], false);
2689  RenderWorld();
2690  RenderPlayer();
2691  RenderSkybox();
2692  RenderFNB();
2693  Trolley();
2694  TrolleyUpdate();
2695  CheckOut();
2696  EscapeSteal();
2697 
2698  modelStack.PushMatrix();
2699  modelStack.Translate(-5,20,-190);
2700  modelStack.Rotate(0,1,0,0);
2701  modelStack.Scale(ExplosionScale,ExplosionScale,ExplosionScale);
2702  if (ExplosionScale < 100 && EscapeEnd == true)
2703  {
2704  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_EXPLODE], true);
2705  }
2706  modelStack.PopMatrix();
2707 
2708  if ( police == true)
2709  {
2710  RenderPolice();
2711  }
2712 
2713  for( int i=0; i < bullet.size(); i ++ )
2714  {
2715  modelStack.PushMatrix();

2717  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_BULLET], true);
2718  modelStack.PopMatrix();
2719  }
2720 
2721  for( int i=0; i < Policebullet.size(); i ++ )
2722  {
2723  modelStack.PushMatrix();
2724  modelStack.Translate(Policebullet[i]->Position.x,Policebullet[i]->Position.y,Policebullet[i]->Position.z);
2725  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_BULLET], true);
2726  modelStack.PopMatrix();
2727  }
2728 
2729  if ( player.trolley == true)
2730  {
2731  modelStack.PushMatrix();
2732  modelStack.Translate(Trolleyz.Position.x,Trolleyz.Position.y,Trolleyz.Position.z);
2733  //RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_BULLET], true);
2734  modelStack.PopMatrix();
2735  }
2736 
2737  if ( camera.getCameraState() == 0 )
2738  RenderScreenUI();
2739  else if (MenuKey == true)
2740  MainMenu();
2741 
2742  if(police == false && Application::IsKeyPressed(VK_TAB))
2743  {
2744  //ShopStaff = true;
2745  RenderItemMissing();
2746  if(UpdateItemMissing == true)
2747  {
2748  UpdateItemMissing = false;
2749  }

2789 void SP2::RenderBasicModel()
2790 {
2791  modelStack.PushMatrix();
2792  modelStack.Translate(0, 1, 0);
2793  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_HEAD], false);
2794  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_BODY], false);
2795  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_LEFTARM], false);
2796  modelStack.PushMatrix();
2797  modelStack.Translate(-3, 0, 0);
2798  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_RIGHTARM], false);
2799  modelStack.PopMatrix();
2800  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_LEFTLEG], false);
2801  modelStack.PushMatrix();
2802  modelStack.Translate(-1, 0, 0);
2803  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_RIGHTLEG], false);
2804  modelStack.PopMatrix();
2805  modelStack.PopMatrix();
2806 }

3148 void SP2::MainMenu()
3149 {
3150  if(MenuKey == true)
3151  { float buttonsize = 20;
3152  //RenderUI(meshList[GEO_TINT], Color(0, 1, 0), 80, 60, 1.5, 40, 30);
3153  RenderUI(meshList[GEO_LOGO], Color(0, 1, 0), 80, 80, 1.5, 40, 50);
3154  //RenderTextOnScreen(meshList[GEO_TEXT], TITLE, Color(0,1,0), 6, 1, 7);
3155  if (MenuState == 1)
3156  {
3157  float middle = 40;
3158  float offset = 25;
3159  RenderUI(meshList[GEO_INSTRUCTIONBTN], Color(0,1,0), 25, 25, 1.5, middle, 25);
3160  RenderUI(meshList[GEO_STARTBTN], Color(0,1,0), buttonsize, buttonsize, 1.5, middle + offset, 25);
3161  }
3162 
3163  else if (MenuState == 2)
3164  {
3165  float middle = 40;
3166  float offset = 25;
3167  RenderUI(meshList[GEO_STARTBTN], Color(0,1,0), 25, 25, 1.5, middle, 25);
3168  RenderUI(meshList[GEO_INSTRUCTIONBTN], Color(0,1,0), buttonsize, buttonsize, 1.5, middle - offset, 25);
3169  RenderUI(meshList[GEO_EXITBTN], Color(0,1,0), buttonsize, buttonsize, 1.5, middle + offset, 25);
3170  }
3171  else if (MenuState == 3)
3172  {
3173  float middle = 40;
3174  float offset = 25;
3175  RenderUI(meshList[GEO_EXITBTN], Color(0,1,0), 25, 25, 1.5, middle, 25);
3176  RenderUI(meshList[GEO_STARTBTN], Color(0,1,0), buttonsize, buttonsize, 1.5, middle - offset, 25);
3177  }

3181 void SP2::MenuUpdate(double dt)
3182 {
3183  if (MenuLimit > 0 )
3184  {
3185  MenuLimit -= (3*dt);
3186  }
3187  if(Application::IsKeyPressed(VK_LEFT))
3188  {
3189  if ( MenuState > 1 && MenuLimit <= 0 )
3190  {
3191  MenuState--;
3192  MenuLimit = true;
3193  MusicPlayer.MetalClank();
3194  }
3195  }
3196  if(Application::IsKeyPressed(VK_RIGHT))
3197  {
3198  if ( MenuState <3 && MenuLimit <= 0)
3199  {
3200  MenuState++;
3201  MenuLimit = true;
3202  MusicPlayer.MetalClank();
3203  }
3204  }
3205  if(Application::IsKeyPressed(VK_BACK) && Instruct == true)
3206  {
3207  camera.setCameraState(2);
3208  Instruct = false;
3209  }
3210 
3211  if(Application::IsKeyPressed(VK_RETURN))
3212  {
3213  if ( MenuState == 1 && MenuLimit <= 0)
3214  {
3215  Instruct = true;
3216  MenuLimit = true;
3217  camera.setCameraState(0);
3218  //MenuKey = false;
3219  }
3220 
3221  else if ( MenuState == 2 && MenuLimit <= 0)
3222  {
3223  camera.setCameraState(0);
3224  MenuLimit = true;
3225  MenuKey = false;
3226  }
3227 
3228  else if ( MenuState == 3 && MenuLimit <= 0)
3229  {
3230  keybd_event( VK_ESCAPE,
3231  0X1B,
3232  KEYEVENTF_EXTENDEDKEY | 0,
3233  0 );
3234 
3235  keybd_event( VK_ESCAPE,
3236  0X1B,
3237  KEYEVENTF_EXTENDEDKEY | 0,
3238  0 );
3239  }
3240  }
3241 
3242  if (MenuKey == true)
3243  {
3244  Lightswitch = 0;
3245  lights[0].power = 0;
3246  lights[1].power = 0;
3247  lights[2].power = 0;
3248  lights[3].power = 0;
3249  lights[4].power = 0;
3250 
3251 
3252  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_LIGHT1_POWER], lights[1].power);
3253  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_LIGHT2_POWER], lights[2].power);
3254  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_LIGHT3_POWER], lights[3].power);
3255  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_LIGHT4_POWER], lights[4].power);
3256  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_LIGHT0_POWER], lights[0].power);
3257  }

3260 void SP2::LightsReset()

3265  lights[1].color.Set(Lightswitch,Lightswitch,Lightswitch);

3267  lights[3].color.Set(Lightswitch,Lightswitch,Lightswitch);
3268  lights[4].color.Set(Lightswitch,Lightswitch,Lightswitch);
3269  lights[0].power = 1.0f;
3270  lights[1].power = 0.2f;
3271  lights[2].power = 0.2f;
3272  lights[3].power = 0.2f;
3273  lights[4].power = 0.2f;

3288 void SP2::ItemMissing()
3289 {
3290  for(int i = 0; i < 5; i++)
3291  {
3292  std::stringstream listitem;
3293  while(RandomItem >= FNB.ReturnListSize())
3294  {
3295  RandomItem = rand() % 1000;
3296  }
3297 
3298  if (FNB.GetRenderPosItem(RandomItem)->getItemAvailability() == true)
3299  {
3300  FNB.GetRenderPosItem(RandomItem)->setItemAvailable(0);
3301  listitem << FNB.GetRenderPosItem(RandomItem)->getItemName();
3302  missinglist = listitem.str();
3303  nameofitem[i] = missinglist;
3304  noofitem[i] = RandomItem;
3305  player.setInventory(FNB.GetRenderPosItem(RandomItem)->getItemName(),FNB.GetRenderPosItem(RandomItem)->getItemPrice());
3306  RandomItem = rand() % 1000;
3307  }
3308  else
3309  {
3310  while(FNB.GetRenderPosItem(RandomItem)->getItemAvailability() == false)
3311  {
3312  RandomItem = rand() % 1000;
3313  while(RandomItem >= FNB.ReturnListSize())
3314  {
3315  RandomItem = rand() % 1000;
3316  }
3317  FNB.GetRenderPosItem(RandomItem)->setItemAvailable(0);
3318  listitem << FNB.GetRenderPosItem(RandomItem)->getItemName();
3319  missinglist = listitem.str();
3320  nameofitem[i] = missinglist;
3321  noofitem[i] = RandomItem;
3322  player.setInventory(FNB.GetRenderPosItem(RandomItem)->getItemName(),FNB.GetRenderPosItem(RandomItem)->getItemPrice());
3323  RandomItem = rand() % 1000;
3324  }
3325  }

3329 void SP2::CheckItem()
3330 {
3331  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('E'))
3332  {
3333  player.Takeitems = true;
3334  }
3335 
3336  if ( player.Takeitems == true)
3337  {
3338  for ( int i = 0; i < FNB.ReturnListSize(); ++i)
3339  {
3340  if ( camera.target.x >= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX()-0.4 && camera.target.x <= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX()+0.4
3341  && camera.target.y >= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationY()-1.2 && camera.target.y <= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationY()+0.8
3342  && camera.target.z >= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ()-1 && camera.target.z <= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ()+1)
3343  {
3344  if (player.returnInvenSize() < player.getInventoryCap() && FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemAvailability() == true && FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() == ItemName)
3345  {
3346  if (ArmSwing < 140 )
3347  {
3348  ArmSwing+=10;
3349  }
3350 
3351  if ( FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() != "Rifle" && FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName() != "Pistol")
3352  {
3353  if (ArmSwing >= 140)
3354  {
3355  FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->setItemAvailable(0);
3356  player.setInventory(FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName(),FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemPrice());
3357  player.Takeitems = false;
3358  break;
3359  }
3360  }
3361  else
3362  {
3363  FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->setItemAvailable(0);
3364  shoot.clip++;
3365  player.Takeitems = false;
3366  break;
3367  }
3368  }
3369  }
3370  }
3371  }
3372  if ( player.Takeitems == false)
3373  {
3374  if (ArmSwing > 0 )
3375  ArmSwing-=2;
3376  }
3377 
3378  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('G'))
3379  {
3380  for ( int i = 0; i < FNB.ReturnListSize(); ++i)
3381  {
3382  if ( camera.target.x >= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX()-0.4 && camera.target.x <= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationX()+0.4
3383  && camera.target.y >= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationY()-1.2 && camera.target.y <= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationY()+0.8
3384  && camera.target.z >= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ()-1 && camera.target.z <= FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemTranslationZ()+1)
3385  {
3386  if (player.returnInvenSize() > 0 && FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemAvailability() == false)
3387  {
3388  for ( int j = 0; j < player.returnInvenSize(); ++j)
3389  {
3390  if ( player.getInventory(j)->getItemName() == FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName())
3391  {
3392  FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->setItemAvailable(1);
3393  player.dropItem(FNB.GetRenderPosItem(i)->getItemName());
3394  break;
3395  }
3396  }
3397  }
3398  }
3399  }
3400  }

3726 void SP2::EscapeSteal()
3727 {
3728  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('E') && player.returnInvenSize() != 0)
3729  {
3730  if ( camera.target.x >= VanBounds[4]->TTL.x && camera.target.x <= VanBounds[4]->TTR.x
3731  && camera.target.y >= VanBounds[4]->BTL.y && camera.target.y <= VanBounds[4]->TTL.y
3732  && camera.target.z >= VanBounds[4]->TBL.z-2 && camera.target.z <= VanBounds[4]->TBL.z+2 && police == true)
3733  {
3734  for ( int i = 0; i <player.returnInvenSize(); ++i)
3735  {
3736  player.setMoney(player.getInventory(i)->getItemPrice()*-1);
3737  player.sellItems(i);
3738  }
3739  }
3740  }
3741  if(Application::IsKeyPressed('E') && player.getMoney() > 0 )
3742  {
3743  if ( camera.target.x >= VanBounds[4]->TTL.x && camera.target.x <= VanBounds[4]->TTR.x
3744  && camera.target.y >= VanBounds[4]->BTL.y && camera.target.y <= VanBounds[4]->TTL.y
3745  && camera.target.z >= VanBounds[4]->TTL.z && camera.target.z <= VanBounds[4]->TBL.z-15 && police == true)
3746  {
3747  //End scene code
3748  EscapeEnd = true;
3749  MusicPlayer.Explosion();
3750  camera.setCameraState(3);
3751 
3752  }
3753  }
3754 }

4109 void SP2::PoliceShoot(double dt)
4110 {
4111  for ( int i = 0; i < PoliceMan.ReadTextFilePoliceSize(); ++i)
4112  {
4113  if ( i == 2)
4114  {

4116  {
4117  if ( PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->ShootCD < 3)
4118  {
4119  PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->ShootCD += (1*dt);
4120  }
4121 
4122  if (PoliceMan.GetRenderPosPolice(i)->ShootCD >= 3)
4123  {

4208 bool SP2::BulletCollision(float x,float y,float z,double dt)

4727 void SP2::RenderCashier()
4728 {
4729  for(int i = 0; i < 4; ++i)
4730  {
4731  modelStack.PushMatrix();
4732  modelStack.Translate(cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getTranslationX(),cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getTranslationY(),cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getTranslationZ());
4733  modelStack.Rotate(cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getRotation(),cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getRX(),cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getRY(),cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getRZ());
4734  modelStack.Scale(cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getScaleX(),cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getScaleY(),cashier.GetRenderPos(i)->getScaleZ());
4735  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_CASHIER], true);
4736  modelStack.PopMatrix();
4737  }
4738 }

4740 void SP2::RenderFridge()
4741 {
4742  for(int i = 0; i < 7; ++i)
4743  {

4745  modelStack.Translate(fridge.GetRenderPos(0)->getTranslationX()-(i*14),fridge.GetRenderPos(0)->getTranslationY(),fridge.GetRenderPos(0)->getTranslationZ());
4746  modelStack.Rotate(fridge.GetRenderPos(0)->getRotation(),fridge.GetRenderPos(0)->getRX(),fridge.GetRenderPos(0)->getRY(),fridge.GetRenderPos(0)->getRZ());
4747  modelStack.Scale(fridge.GetRenderPos(0)->getScaleX(),fridge.GetRenderPos(0)->getScaleY(),fridge.GetRenderPos(0)->getScaleZ());
4748  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_FRIDGE], true);

4753 void SP2::RenderShelves()
4754 {
4755  int temp = 0;
4756  for(int i = 1; i <= 3; ++ i )
4757  {
4758  for(int j = 0; j < 12; ++ j )
4759  {
4760  if ( j >= 4 && j < 8 )
4761  {
4762  temp = 10;
4763  }
4764  else if ( j >= 8 )
4765  {
4766  temp = 20;
4767  }
4768  else
4769  {
4770  temp = 0;
4771  }
4772 
4773  modelStack.PushMatrix();
4774  modelStack.Translate(shelve.GetRenderPos(0)->getTranslationX()+(j*6)+temp,shelve.GetRenderPos(0)->getTranslationY(),shelve.GetRenderPos(0)->getTranslationZ()+(i*15));
4775  modelStack.Rotate(shelve.GetRenderPos(0)->getRotation(),shelve.GetRenderPos(0)->getRX(),shelve.GetRenderPos(0)->getRY(),shelve.GetRenderPos(0)->getRZ());
4776  modelStack.Scale(shelve.GetRenderPos(0)->getScaleX(),shelve.GetRenderPos(0)->getScaleY(),shelve.GetRenderPos(0)->getScaleZ());
4777  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_SHELF], true);
4778  modelStack.PopMatrix();
4779  }
4780  }
4781 }

4783 void SP2::RenderWorld()
4784 {

4786  modelStack.Translate(data.GetRenderPos(0)->getTranslationX(),data.GetRenderPos(0)->getTranslationY(),data.GetRenderPos(0)->getTranslationZ());
4787  modelStack.Rotate(data.GetRenderPos(0)->getRotation(),data.GetRenderPos(0)->getRX(),data.GetRenderPos(0)->getRY(),data.GetRenderPos(0)->getRZ());

4789  RenderMesh(meshList[GEO_MODEL_MART], true);
4790

4792  modelStack.Translate(EntranceDoorSlide,data.GetRenderPos(1)->getTranslationY(),data.GetRenderPos(1)->getTranslationZ());
4793  modelStack.Rotate(data.GetRenderPos(1)->getRotation(),data.GetRenderPos(1)->getRX(),data.GetRenderPos(1)->getRY(),data.GetRenderPos(1)->getRZ());
4794  modelStack.Scale(data.GetRenderPos(1)->getScaleX(),data.GetRenderPos(1)->getScaleY(),data.GetRenderPos(1)->getScaleZ());

4797

5156 void SP2::RenderPlayer()
5157 {
5158  if (police != true && EscapeEnd != true)
5159  {
5160  //Origin
5161  modelStack.PushMatrix();
5162  modelStack.Translate(camera.position.x, camera.position.y, camera.position.z);
5163  //Left Right to camera
5164  if ( player.trolley == false)
5165  modelStack.Rotate(DupeRotArms,0,1,0);
5166  else if ( player.trolley == true)
5167  modelStack.Rotate(DupeRot,0,1,0);
5168  modelStack.PushMatrix();
5169  //Up Down to camera
5170  if ( player.trolley == false)
5171  modelStack.Rotate(DupeRotArmsY,1,0,0);
5172  /*else if ( player.trolley == true)
5173  modelStack.Rotate(-60,1,0,0);*/
5174  //Right Arm
5175  modelStack.PushMatrix();
5176  modelStack.Translate(0.05, -0.2, -0.1);
5177  //modelStack.Translate(0.05, -0.2, -0.1);
5178  modelStack.Rotate(-10,0,1,0);
5179  modelStack.PushMatrix();
5180  modelStack.Rotate(ArmSwing,1,0,0);
5181  if ( player.trolley == false)

5596 
5597 void SP2::RenderMesh(Mesh *mesh, bool enableLight)
5598 {
5599  Mtx44 MVP, modelView, modelView_inverse_transpose;
5600 
5601  MVP = projectionStack.Top() * viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top();
5602  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MVP], 1, GL_FALSE, &MVP.a[0]);
5603  if(enableLight)
5604  {
5605  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_LIGHTENABLED], 1);
5606  modelView = viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top();
5607  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MODELVIEW], 1, GL_FALSE, &modelView.a[0]);
5608  modelView_inverse_transpose = modelView.GetInverse().GetTranspose();
5609  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MODELVIEW_INVERSE_TRANSPOSE], 1, GL_FALSE, &modelView_inverse_transpose.a[0]);
5610 
5611  //load material
5612  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_AMBIENT], 1, &mesh->material.kAmbient.r);
5613  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_DIFFUSE], 1, &mesh->material.kDiffuse.r);
5614  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_SPECULAR], 1, &mesh->material.kSpecular.r);
5615  glUniform1f(m_parameters[U_MATERIAL_SHININESS], mesh->material.kShininess);
5616  }
5617  else
5618  {
5619  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_LIGHTENABLED], 0);
5620  }
5621 
5622  //mesh->Render();
5623 
5624  if(mesh->textureID > 0)
5625  {
5626  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE_ENABLED], 1);
5627  glActiveTexture(GL_TEXTURE0);
5628  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, mesh->textureID);
5629  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE], 0);
5630  }
5631  else
5632  {
5633  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE_ENABLED], 0);
5634  }
5635  mesh->Render(); //this line should only be called once
5636  if(mesh->textureID > 0)
5637  {
5638  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, 0);
5639  }
5640 }
5641 
5642 void SP2::RenderText(Mesh* mesh, std::string text, Color color)
5643 {
5644  if(!mesh || mesh->textureID <= 0) //Proper error check
5645  return;
5646 
5647  glDisable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
5648  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_TEXT_ENABLED], 1);
5649  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_TEXT_COLOR], 1, &color.r);
5650  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_LIGHTENABLED], 0);
5651  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE_ENABLED], 1);
5652  glActiveTexture(GL_TEXTURE0);
5653  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, mesh->textureID);
5654  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE], 0);
5655  for(unsigned i = 0; i < text.length(); ++i)
5656  {
5657  Mtx44 characterSpacing;
5658  characterSpacing.SetToTranslation(i * 1.0f, 0, 0); //1.0f is the spacing of each character, you may change this value
5659  Mtx44 MVP = projectionStack.Top() * viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top() * characterSpacing;
5660  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MVP], 1, GL_FALSE, &MVP.a[0]);
5661 
5662  mesh->Render((unsigned)text[i] * 6, 6);
5663  }
5664  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, 0);
5665  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_TEXT_ENABLED], 0);
5666  glEnable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
5667 }
5668 
5669 void SP2::RenderTextOnScreen(Mesh* mesh, std::string text, Color color, float size, float x, float y)
5670 {
5671  if(!mesh || mesh->textureID <= 0) //Proper error check
5672  return;
5673 
5674 
5675  glDisable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
5676 
5677  Mtx44 ortho;
5678  ortho.SetToOrtho(0, 80, 0, 60, -10, 10); //size of screen UI
5679  projectionStack.PushMatrix();
5680  projectionStack.LoadMatrix(ortho);
5681  viewStack.PushMatrix();
5682  viewStack.LoadIdentity(); //No need camera for ortho mode
5683  modelStack.PushMatrix();
5684  modelStack.LoadIdentity(); //Reset modelStack
5685  modelStack.Scale(size, size, size);
5686  modelStack.Translate(x, y, 0);
5687 
5688  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_TEXT_ENABLED], 1);
5689  glUniform3fv(m_parameters[U_TEXT_COLOR], 1, &color.r);
5690  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_LIGHTENABLED], 0);
5691  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE_ENABLED], 1);
5692  glActiveTexture(GL_TEXTURE0);
5693  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, mesh->textureID);
5694  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_COLOR_TEXTURE], 0);
5695  for(unsigned i = 0; i < text.length(); ++i)
5696  {
5697  Mtx44 characterSpacing;
5698  characterSpacing.SetToTranslation(i * 1.0f+1.5f, 1.0f, 0); //1.0f is the spacing of each character, you may change this value
5699  Mtx44 MVP = projectionStack.Top() * viewStack.Top() * modelStack.Top() * characterSpacing;
5700  glUniformMatrix4fv(m_parameters[U_MVP], 1, GL_FALSE, &MVP.a[0]);
5701 
5702  mesh->Render((unsigned)text[i] * 6, 6);
5703  }
5704  glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, 0);
5705  glUniform1i(m_parameters[U_TEXT_ENABLED], 0);
5706  projectionStack.PopMatrix();
5707  viewStack.PopMatrix();
5708  modelStack.PopMatrix();
5709 
5710  glEnable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
5711 }
5712 
5713 void SP2::RenderUI(Mesh* mesh, Color color, float sizeX,float sizeY,float sizeZ, float x, float y)
5714 {
5715  if(!mesh || mesh->textureID <= 0) //Proper error check
5716  return;
5717 
5718 
5719  glDisable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
5720 
5721  Mtx44 ortho;
5722  ortho.SetToOrtho(0, 80, 0, 60, -10, 10); //size of screen UI
5723  projectionStack.PushMatrix();
5724  projectionStack.LoadMatrix(ortho);
5725  viewStack.PushMatrix();
5726  viewStack.LoadIdentity(); //No need camera for ortho mode
5727  modelStack.PushMatrix();
5728  modelStack.LoadIdentity(); //Reset modelStack
5729  modelStack.Translate(x, y, 0);
5730  modelStack.Scale(sizeX, sizeY, sizeZ);
5731 
5732  RenderMesh(mesh, false);
5733  projectionStack.PopMatrix();
5734  viewStack.PopMatrix();
5735  modelStack.PopMatrix();
5736 
5737  glEnable(GL_DEPTH_TEST);
5738 }
5739 
5740 void SP2::Exit()
5741 {
5742  // Cleanup here
